          <li>Fixes a memory leak when reloading CSS (Lars Windolf)</li>
          <li>Fixes CVE-2023-1350: RCE vulnerability on feed enrichment (patch by Alexander Erwin Ittner)</li>
          <li>Fixes #1200: Crash on double free (mozbugbox)</li>
